23:45.162 --> 23:48.127
So let's not get too uptight here about terminology.

23:50.050 --> 23:57.000
You've gone to church your whole life, your vast Jesus to save you and all, but you don't really know God like this.

23:59.464 --> 24:01.126
And I have days when I don't know I'm like this.

24:02.228 --> 24:03.049
I'm just being honest.

24:04.431 --> 24:11.762
I have days when I'm hiding behind the bush, ashamed for fear, because I've done something wrong.

24:13.602 --> 24:14.503
I do things wrong.

24:19.570 --> 24:22.574
But you don't know that he's there, a loving father.

24:22.614 --> 24:40.178
And he's not, I mean, I'm a father, three beautiful kids, big kids now, but if I ever had a problem and they came to me and said, Dad, I can't do this.

24:41.634 --> 24:43.316
I'm not making anything up this.

24:43.376 --> 24:44.096
It's not working.

24:44.116 --> 24:46.038
And I just keep on over and over again.

24:46.639 --> 24:50.723
What kind of a dad would I be if I said, get out of my sight.

24:51.443 --> 24:55.747
You have filthy rotten child.

24:57.189 --> 24:58.010
What kind of a father?

24:58.730 --> 25:01.493
That's the god some of us have.

25:01.513 --> 25:02.814
But it's not the god of the Bible.

25:04.356 --> 25:10.962
The god of the Bible is the father that runs and embraces a stinking filthy son covered in pig swill.

25:11.874 --> 25:16.279
Kisses him on the neck and throws your robe around his filth and throws a party for him at home.

25:18.001 --> 25:18.821
And brings him back.

25:20.163 --> 25:21.965
Celebrating.

25:21.985 --> 25:27.611
That's our God.

25:27.631 --> 25:29.913
Who wants to have our relationship with that God?

25:33.017 --> 25:33.637
Put your hand up.

25:33.998 --> 25:35.099
I don't care how long you've been.

25:35.540 --> 25:38.082
Inverted comments saved.

25:38.102 --> 25:39.404
Put your hand up and down again.

25:39.784 --> 25:40.425
God bless you.

25:41.005 --> 25:41.586
God bless you.

25:43.522 --> 25:44.183
God bless you.

25:47.747 --> 25:48.468
Thank you Lord.

25:49.129 --> 25:49.890
Thank you Lord.

25:50.911 --> 25:56.979
Thank you that it's all about you Father and Lord I really do not want to misrepresent you.

25:58.701 --> 26:05.449
Forgive me because I have done over the years I'm absolutely sure of it and I hope I haven't done tonight in any way.

26:07.011 --> 26:12.498
But I thank you that God is love and God is light.

26:13.634 --> 26:16.538
And in him is no darkness at all.

26:18.060 --> 26:18.901
No darkness.

26:20.103 --> 26:23.127
No shadow of turning.

26:27.513 --> 26:30.498
Thank you that perfect love drives out fair.

26:31.940 --> 26:39.711
For fear has to do with punishment, but the ever has been made perfect in love.

26:41.473 --> 26:42.194
Does not fear.

26:44.418 --> 26:46.100
O Lord, deliver us from fear.

26:47.201 --> 26:50.524
For you have not given us a spirit of fear, but power, love, and a sound mind.

26:51.625 --> 27:02.576
You've not been given a spirit of bondage again to fear, but the spirit of adoption by which you cry out, Abba, Abba, Father, Papa, Daddy, Daddy in heaven, Father in heaven, Abba.

27:05.399 --> 27:05.859
Thank you.

27:06.259 --> 27:12.946
Thank you, Jesus, that you lifted us to that place to have such a relationship with our Father God, your Father.

27:13.378 --> 27:19.586
And you can say to us, I'm going to your Father and my Father, to your God and my God.

27:19.606 --> 27:20.027
Thank you.

27:20.267 --> 27:21.849
Thank you, you've brought us in, Lord Jesus.

27:23.271 --> 27:27.277
Let not our shame, sin and fear shut aside, because it's all I.

27:29.119 --> 27:32.203
And I pray that those lives will crumble, those strongholds will crumble.

27:32.704 --> 27:38.111
And Lord, if you deliver Jesus for so high, shall you not freely with Him give us all things.

27:38.171 --> 27:43.058
And so may people come tonight for healing, physical, mental, emotional, spiritual healing.

27:43.458 --> 27:45.884
and know the wonder of the power of the gospel.

27:46.285 --> 27:49.252
Thank you, Lord, that it's good news.

27:50.334 --> 27:52.640
Lord, we're tired of the bad news.

27:54.103 --> 27:55.206
We need the good news.

27:57.792 --> 27:58.514
Thank you, Jesus.

